<h1>Password updated</h1>
<p>Hi <strong>{{fullName}}</strong>,</p>

<div class="surface surface-success">
  <p><strong>Your {{appName}} password was changed successfully.</strong></p>
  <p>Time: <strong>{{timestamp}}</strong></p>
</div>

<p style="margin-top: 16px;">If you made this change, no further action is needed.</p>

<hr class="divider">

<div class="surface surface-error">
  <h2>Did not change your password?</h2>
  <p>Your account may be compromised. Reset your password in the app right away and contact support if you need help.</p>
</div>
